snippet.title: No prince needed - Android Release Trailer
snippet.description:
No prince needed is an adorable 2D puzzle platformer where you play as a princess which was kidnapped by evil wizard. Use ability to throw boxes and solve unique puzzles. Escape the castle with the power of your intelligence and platforming skills!

Link: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ArmedPandaGames.Noprinceneeded
